</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BB05E5A021D4A5155817DD6FE72F898" blockId="26.[151,1436,1483,1796]" pageId="26" pageNumber="27">
Comments: Some of the 
<taxonomicName id="4C0F25D9021D4A5154A17DD7FDA1F927" baseAuthorityName="Herrich-Schaffer" baseAuthorityYear="1848" box="[487,608,1701,1724]" class="Insecta" family="Belostomatidae" genus="Belostoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="26" pageNumber="27" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="anurum">
<emphasis id="B97B8248021D4A5154A17DD7FDA1F927" box="[487,608,1701,1724]" italics="true" pageId="26" pageNumber="27">B. anurum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
specimens studied so far do not differ from 
<taxonomicName id="4C0F25D9021D4A5151217DD7FE91F944" authority="(Palisot de Beauvois, 1805)" baseAuthorityName="Palisot de Beauvois" baseAuthorityYear="1805" class="Insecta" family="Belostomatidae" genus="Belostoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="26" pageNumber="27" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="subspinosum">
<emphasis id="B97B8248021D4A5151217DD7FAD8F927" box="[1127,1305,1700,1724]" italics="true" pageId="26" pageNumber="27">B. subspinosum</emphasis>
(Palisot de Beauvois, 1805)
</taxonomicName>
subspecies in features of the phallus, and 
<taxonomicName id="4C0F25D9021D4A5156717DBBFC6EF97B" baseAuthorityName="Herrich-Schaffer" baseAuthorityYear="1848" box="[823,943,1737,1760]" class="Insecta" family="Belostomatidae" genus="Belostoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="26" pageNumber="27" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="anurum">
<emphasis id="B97B8248021D4A5156717DBBFC6EF97B" box="[823,943,1737,1760]" italics="true" pageId="26" pageNumber="27">B. anurum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
might eventually prove to be a junior-synonym of 
<taxonomicName id="4C0F25D9021D4A5155BA7D9FFE6DF89F" baseAuthorityName="Palisot de Beauvois" baseAuthorityYear="1805" box="[252,428,1772,1796]" class="Insecta" family="Belostomatidae" genus="Belostoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="26" pageNumber="27" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="subspinosum">
<emphasis id="B97B8248021D4A5155BA7D9FFE6DF89F" box="[252,428,1772,1796]" italics="true" pageId="26" pageNumber="27">B. subspinosum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
